835
00:53:46,348 --> 00:53:47,974
Jujurlah kepadanya.

836
00:53:49,017 --> 00:53:50,185
Selamat malam.

837
00:53:53,563 --> 00:53:55,106
- Hei, Dan!
- Hei!

838
00:53:55,190 --> 00:53:59,236
