00:54:50,912 --> 00:54:53,873
- Baik. Sepakat.
- Apa kau mau handuk…

858
00:54:54,499 --> 00:54:56,960
Jangan ajak orang biasa bicara.

859
00:54:57,043 --> 00:54:58,503
